300bc27b01","tid":2097211,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f6be1d5f513a31aef77bcb7dbd82083e7a46961","tid":2097211,"uid":350338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd25fee09e63242e555613f03db6125b556c1707","tid":2097211,"uid":32712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"用緊，識收邊就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"要點樣收邊 求賜教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T22:55:10.000Z","msg":"都係用地腳線遮姐"},{"pid":"126e5834d6b88033465a3a610fba9d13b8ec9788","tid":2097211,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:05:36.000Z","msg":"ikea有<br />\n一般來講，放好膠底就可以一條一條上<br />\n用閘機cut短<br />\n<br />\ndiy唔難，不過一般都係地下唔平，行過有聲"},{"pid":"b621ff541ee397ec7ad3f36d5afe72be6fecf6b5","tid":2097211,"uid":51109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"無逢地板要用線鋸機 同 釘槍（做地腳線）<br />\n<br />\n線鋸機少心d就得<br />\n<br />\n下面鋪層珍珠綿"},{"pid":"e6ac39259c5b017a917a72686b664c21ada490e9","tid":2097211,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926751fa695724db2ae8a29de991c32680c383ab","tid":2097211,"uid":361277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"我完全唔會用呢種地板，因為佢個設計係一塊扣一塊，而達至無縫效果，聽落好似幾好<br />\n但有幾樣野要留意<br />\n1）地台如果唔平，鋪完後行上去會有聲<br />\n2）防水功能成疑，建議自己淘幾耐浸下水先<br />\n3）香港天氣潮濕，冬夏溫差大，用呢隻地板，好易有熱脹冷縮，如果你鋪得貼牆邊，熱脹時有機會谷起，留太多虛位，冷縮時又見到條La，手工同經驗要求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n最後一樣係最重要！！！<br />\n佢個一塊扣一塊設計會令到第日完全維修唔到，假設你其中一塊有問題，想換，你係冇可能單獨起咗其中一塊更換<br />\n<br />\nGBU<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc82ee3fcced50196ff3eb02e908736df55248b","tid":2097211,"uid":350338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6ac39259c5b017a917a72686b664c21ada490e9","tid":2097211,"uid":26675,